cff-version: 1.2.0
title: NHS Clinical Safety Skills for Claude Code
message: >-
  If you use this resource in your research, teaching, or publications,
  please cite it using the metadata below.
type: dataset
authors:
  - name: Clinical Quality Artificial Intelligence (CQAI)
    website: https://github.com/Clinical-Quality-Artifical-Intelligence
abstract: >-
  An open educational resource providing AI-assisted clinical safety skills
  for student nurses, newly qualified nurses, and Digital Clinical Safety
  Officers (DCSOs). Covers DCB0129, DCB0160, hazard logs, safety cases,
  ML/AI safety, and FHIR compliance. Available in 10 languages.
keywords:
  - clinical safety
  - DCB0129
  - DCB0160
  - nursing education
  - digital clinical safety officer
  - NHS
  - health IT
  - patient safety
  - hazard log
  - Claude Code
